There are several suspicious processes with open sockets in the provided data:

1. Process ID 888 (firefox.exe) has an open socket with a remote address 66.249.91.104 on port 80.
2. Process ID 1244 (spoolsv.exe) has open sockets with remote addresses 193.104.22.71 and 192.168.0.1 on port 80 and 30379 respectively.
3. Process ID 4 (System) has an open socket with a remote address 192.168.0.176 on port 139.
4. Process ID 880 (svchost.exe) has an open socket with a remote address 0.0.0.0 on port 1185.

These processes and their corresponding network connections should be further investigated as they may indicate suspicious or unauthorized activities.
